Class WeaponCard

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.WeaponCard
  • public class WeaponCard
extends java.lang.Object
    The following class is supposed to extend Card by adding another type of Cards known as WeaponCards There are 21 WeaponCards each different from the other. These cards are to be used during Gameplay to inflict damage to the adversary.
